s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eusers%20that%20they%20can%20melt%20eggs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20as%20disconnected%20executives%20replace%20human%20editors%20with%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F11%2F02%2Ftech%2Fmicrosoft-ai-news%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20Microsoft%20did%20with%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FMSN.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMSN.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F11%2F02%2Ftech%2Fmicrosoft-ai-news%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2C%20leading%20to%20misinformation%20delivered%20to%20over%20a%20billion%20people%20a%20month%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20we'll%20enter%20a%20cycle%20where%20the%20generative%20models%20train%20themselves%20on%20the%20remains%20of%20an%20internet%20poisoned%20by%20generative%20content.%20Even%20the%20supposedly%20human%20domain%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-media-flooded-spammy-ai-content-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%20has%20become%20flooded%20with%20AI%20spam%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20turning%20X%2C%20Facebook%2C%20Reddit%2C%20and%20Instagram%20into%20a%20constant%20battle%20against%20misinformation%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkrebsonsecurity.com%2F2023%2F05%2Finterview-with-a-crypto-scam-investment-spammer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoutright%20scams%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20generative%20AI%20is%20just%20the%20newest%20extension%20of%20the%20algorithm%2C%20it%20poses%20a%20unique%20threat.%20Before%2C%20humans%20controlled%20the%20inputs%20and%20set%20rules%20of%20engagement%20for%20the%20models%20while%20the%20computers%20produced%20the%20output.%20Now%20we're%20allowing%20these%20models%20to%20set%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20game%20for%20us%2C%20generating%20both%20the%20inputs%20and%20outputs.%20We're%20already%20starting%20to%20see%20some%20of%20the%20deleterious%20effects%3A%20In%202023%2C%20the%20National%20Eating%20Disorders%20Association%20replaced%20its%20human%20helpline%20staff%20with%20an%20AI%20chatbot%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2Fsections%2Fhealth-shots%2F2023%2F06%2F08%2F1180838096%2Fan-eating-disorders-chatbot-offered-dieting-advice-raising-fears-about-ai-in-hea%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonly%20to%20have%20to%20pull%20it%20shortly%20thereafter%20when%20it%20started%20giving%20harmful%20weight-loss%20advice%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wealthy%20and%20powerful%20will%20be%20able%20to%20opt%20out%20of%20this%20algorithmically%20driven%20future%20or%20shape%20it%20in%20their%20image%20by%20connecting%20directly%20to%20the%20humans%20behind%20companies%20shrouded%20by%20algorithmic%20processes.%20When%20you%20have%20a%20private%20banker%2C%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20worry%20about%20an%20anonymous%2C%20automated%20financial%20review%20%E2%80%94%20you've%20got%20a%20person%20with%20an%20email%20address%20and%20a%20phone%20number.%20The%20wealthy%20won't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fkatiejennings%2F2023%2F07%2F17%2Fthis-ai-chatbot-has-helped-doctors-treat-3-million-people%2F%3Fsh%3D9fc6cd14cea2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enurses%20or%20doctors%20being%20replaced%20by%20AI%20processes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20because%20they'll%20be%20able%20to%20afford%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpress.aboutamazon.com%2F2022%2F7%2Famazon-and-one-medical-sign-an-agreement-for-amazon-to-acquire-one-medical%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econcierge%20medical%20services%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20powerful%20won't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20their%20jobs%20being%20automated%20away%20because%20they'll%20be%20the%20ones%20choosing%20where%20and%20when%20a%20job%20is%20handed%20over%20to%20an%20automated%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20rest%20of%20us%2C%20it%20seems%20as%20if%20more%20and%20more%20of%20our%20lives%20will%20be%