n't%20know%20in%20what%20field%20or%20how%2C%20but%20I%20remember%20thinking%20to%20myself%2C%20%3Cem%3EI'm%20an%20entrepreneur%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20attended%20the%20University%20of%20Florida%2C%20there%20was%20a%20brief%20moment%20(maybe%20a%20few%20hours%20and%20a%20Greyhound%20bus%20ride%20home)%20when%20I%20contemplated%20dropping%20out%20of%20college%2C%20but%20I%20didn't.%20Instead%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20change%20my%20major%20from%20business%20to%20event%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20bet%20on%20myself.%20I%20secured%20an%20internship%20during%20my%20senior%20year%20of%20college%20at%20the%20White%20House%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fobama-100-days-president-2016-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehistorical%20Obama%20administration%20in%202010%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Eventually%2C%20after%20a%20decade%20of%20assisting%20high-profile%20public%20figures%20and%20executives%20to%20make%20their%20lives%20easier%2C%20my%20boss%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Michelle%20Obama%2C%20planted%20the%20seed%20for%20me%20to%20start%20my%20own%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeing%20an%20advance%20associate%20in%20the%20White%20House%20gave%20me%20the%20opportunity%20to%20use%20both%20of%20my%20degrees%20at%20once%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20assigned%20to%20work%20in%20the%20presidential%20scheduling%20and%20advance%20office%20for%20my%20internship.%20But%20after%20I%20completed%20my%20degrees%2C%20double%20majoring%20in%20event%20management%20and%20political%20science%20with%20a%20minor%20in%20business%2C%20I%20returned%20back%20to%20the%20White%20House%20as%20an%20advance%20associate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Clayton%20with%20Michelle%20Obama%20and%20colleagues%20in%20the%20Rose%20Garden%20before%20a%202016%20College%20Signing%20Day%20event.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660b3e723f923f7dab0366cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EClayton%20with%20Michelle%20Obama%20and%20colleagues%20in%20the%20Rose%20Garden%20before%20a%202016%20College%20Signing%20Day%20event.%3Cp%3EChuck%20Kennedy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20see%20the%20president%20or%20the%20first%20lady%20on%20TV%20delivering%20a%20speech%2C%20talking%20to%20kids%2C%20visiting%20a%20disaster%20site%2C%20meeting%20with%20heads%20of%20state%20overseas%2C%20or%20even%20going%20on%20a%20family%20bike%20ride%2C%20those%20details%20are%20accounted%20for%20and%20intricately%20planned%20by%20an%20advance%20team%20in%20coordination%20with%20secret%20service%20and%20military%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvance%20provided%20me%20with%20the%20opportunity%20to%20use%20both%20of%20my%20degrees%20at%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20became%20former%20First%20Lady%20Michelle%20Obama's%20body%20person%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20hard%20work%20didn't%20go%20unnoticed%2C%20while%20in%20my%20role%20as%20an%20advance%20associate.%20I%20was%20recommended%20to%20apply%20and%20secured%20an%20administrative%20position%20in%20Disney's%20government%20relations%20office%2C%20supporting%20C-Suite%20executives%20in%20the%20nation's%20capital%20before%20returning%20to%20the%20White%20House%20to%20become%20the%20%26quot%3Bbody%20person%26quot%3B%20for%20former%20First%20Lady%20Michelle%20Obama%20during%20her%20second%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20body%20person%20is%20an%20assistant%20who%20is%20quite%20literally%20the%20right%20hand%20to%20a%20political%20figure%2C%20following%20them%20around%20the%20clock%20and%20accompanying%20them%3Cem%3E%20everywhere%3C%2Fem%3E.%20They%20anticipate%20their%20principal's%20every%20move.%20In%20this%20capacity%2C%20I%20helped%20Mrs.%20Obama%20connect%20with%20communities%20around%20the%20world.%20I%20ensured%20every%20detail%20of%20her%20personal%20and%20public-facing%20events%20was%20executed%20flawlessly%2C%20directing%20teams%20who%20coordinated%20her%20domestic%20and%20international%20engagements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chynna%20Clayton%20assisting%20Michelle%20Obama%20behind-the-scene%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660ada563f923f7dab031330%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EClayton%20assisting%20Michelle%20Obama%20backstage%20before%20a%20%26quot%3BWhen%20We%20All%20Vote%26quot%3B%20rally%20in%202018.%3Cp%3EChuck%20Kennedy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20President%20Barack%20Obama's%20term%20ended%20in%20January%202017%2C%20I%20was%20retained%20by%20the%20personal%20office%20of%20Barack%20and%20Michelle%20Obama%20as%20their%20director%20of%20travel%20and%20event%20operations.%20I%20helped%20manage%20their%20family's%20personal%20obligations%20while%20overseeing%20the%20coordination%20of%20Mrs.%20Obama's%20engagement%20until%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMichelle%20Obama%20gave%20me%20the%20ultimate%20vote%20of%20confidence%20to%20start%20my%20business%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMrs.%20Obama%20was%20the%20person%20who%20planted%20the%20seed%20for%20me%20to%20start%20my%20business.%20She%20made%20a%20statement%20that%20stuck%20with%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20in%20my%20friend%20group%20reaches%20out%20to%20you%20when%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20find%20an%20assistant%20%E2%80%A6%20so%20Chynna%2C%20'there%20is%20a%20there%20%E2%80%A6%20there!'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20ultimate%20vote%20of%20confidence%20coming%20from%20someone%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopen.spotify.com%2Fepisode%2F7s1IzRGuYs2kMubG15d9P0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elooked%20up%20to%20as%20my%20mentor%3C%2Fa%3E.%20With%20the%20help%20of%20a%20few%20friends%20who%20knew%20how%20to%20set%20up%20a%20business%2C%20some%20strategic%20planning%2C%20a%20little%20soul-searching%2C%20and%20a%20notebook%20full%20of%20ideas%2C%20I%20launched%20Matriarch%20Made%20Development%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20company%20focuses%20on%20business%20development%2C%20personnel%20development%2C%20and%20personal%20development.%20Essentially%2C%20I%20help%20executives%2C%20celebrities%2C%20government%20officials%2C%20heads%20of%20human%20resources%20departments%2C%20and%20business%20owners%20find%20assistants.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20help%20with%20continued%20assistant%20training%20and%20development%20and%20consulting%20on%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20have%20six%20tips%20for%20anyone%20ready%20to%20become%20an%20entrepreneur%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20quick%20tips%20I'd%20share%20with%20anyone%20who's%20ready%20to%20materialize%20their%20dreams%20of%20entrepreneurship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EBaby%20steps.%20It%20takes%20time%20and%20hustle%20to%20get%20clientele%20and%20keep%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EGive%20yourself%20grace%20and%20be%20patient%20with%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3ETry%20to%20maintain%20a%20job%20on%20the%20side%20that%20will%20ensure%20you%20have%20a%20consistent%20paycheck%2C%20before%20diving%20headfirst%20into%20entrepreneurship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EInvest%20in%20a%20contract%20lawyer%20and%20accountant.%20It's%20the%20best%20thing%20you%20can%20do%20for%20yourself%20and%20your%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EPlease%20set%20aside%2030%20to%2035%25%20of%20your%20revenue%20for%20your%20taxes.%20Do%20not%20play%20with%20Uncle%20Sam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20OK%20to%20fail.%20Every%20business%20will%20not%20be%20a%20million-dollar%20one.%20Sometimes%20the%20audacity%20is%20what%20makes%20the%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20business%20honors%20four%20generations%20of%20maternal%20women%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20name%20my%20business%2C%20Matriarch%20Made%20Development%2C%20in%20honor%20of%20the%20four%20generations%20of%20maternal%20women%20who%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20me%20to%20become%20who%20I%20am%3A%20My%20mother%2C%20my%20grandmother%2C%20my%20great-grandmother%2C%20and%20my%20great-aunt.%20I'm%20forever%20indebted%20and%20grateful%20for%20the%20lessons%20they%20taught%20me%2C%20and%20use%20them%20daily%20as%20an%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20really%20have%20to%20credit%20my%20late%20aunt%20Linder%20Williams%20for%20introducing%20me%20to%20entrepreneurship%20and%20event%20planning.%20She%20was%20so%20creative%2C%20resourceful%2C%20and%20our%20family%20event%20planner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221321%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chynna%20Clayton%20with%20family%20and%20at%20work.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660ad9bd1caec1275a6b4da6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221269%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETop%20photo%3A%20Clayton%20posing%20with%20Linder%20Williams%20(Great%20Aunt)%2C%20Margaret%20Berry%20(Great%20Grandmother)%2C%20Mildred%20King%20(Grandmother)%2C%20Doris%20King%20(Mother)%20in%20Kathleen%2C%20Georgia%20%7C%20Bottom%20Photo%3A%20Clayton%20with%20colleagues%20in%20the%20White%20House.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Chynna%20Clayton%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20aunt%20would%20take%20me%20with%20her%20as%20a%20kid%20to%20wholesale%20shops%20and%20allow%20me%20to%20assist%20her%20in%20scouring%20clearance%20racks%20for%20items%20that%20we'd%20later%20beautifully%20package%20and%20sell%20on%20the%20corners%20of%20Miami%20for%20holidays%20like%20Valentine's%20Day%2C%20Mother's%20or%20Father's%20Day%2C%20and%20Easter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20if%20my%20late%20aunt%20could%20add%20one%20tip%20to%20my%20list%20for%20aspiring%20or%20current%20entrepreneurs%2C%20she'd%20say%20shop%20the%20day%20after%20a%20holiday%20to%20get%20the%20best%20deals%20ahead%20of%20the%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%