%20about%20Lee%20Byung%20Hun%20and%20Son%20Ye%20Jin's%20potential%20collaboration%20with%20Park%20Chan%20Wook.%20Offers%20were%20extended%20through%20BH%20Entertainment%20and%20MSteam%20Entertainment%2C%20sparking%20anticipation%20for%20a%20reunion%20and%20Son%20Ye%20Jin's%20debut%20collaboration%20with%20the%20director.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fson-ye-jin-and-lee-byung-hun-to-join-forces-for-park-chan-wooks-upcoming-thriller%2Farticleshow%2F108970247.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sand%20Substitute%20Developed%20By%20Indian%20Experts%20For%20Eco-Friendly%20Construction%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EScientists%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Science%20(IISc)%20in%20Bengaluru%20have%20created%20a%20promising%20new%20material%20that%20can%20replace%20natural%20sand%20in%20construction.%20This%20development%20comes%20as%20a%20response%20to%20the%20growing%20scarcity%20of%20sand%2C%20a%20crucial%20component%20in%20building%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20at%20IISc's%20Centre%20for%20Sustainable%20Technologies%20(CST)%20is%20exploring%20methods%20to%20utilise%20carbon%20dioxide%20(CO2)%20captured%20from%20industrial%20waste%20gases.%20They%20treat%20excavated%20soil%20and%20construction%20waste%20with%20this%20CO2%2C%20transforming%20it%20into%20a%20viable%20sand%20alternative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20materials%20can%20then%20be%20used%20to%20partially%20replace%20natural%20sand.%20This%20would%20not%20only%20reduce%20the%20environmental%20impact%20of%20construction%20materials%20but%20also%20impart%20properties%20that%20can%20enhance%20their%20use%20for%20construction%2C%26quot%3B%20stated%20IISc%20in%20a%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiisc.ac.in%2Fevents%2Fpaving-new-paths-for-sustainable-construction%2F%5C%22%3Epress%20release.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELed%20by%20Assistant%20Professor%20Souradeep%20Gupta%2C%20the%20research%20demonstrates%20that%20using%20CO2-treated%20construction%20waste%20in%20mortar%2C%20followed%20by%20curing%20in%20a%20CO2-rich%20environment%2C%20significantly%20accelerates%20the%20development%20of%20the%20material's%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20lab%20members%20are%20seen%20surrounding%20the%20developed%20carbon-sequestered%20building%20materials%2C%20which%20were%20manufactured%20using%20additive%20manufacturing.%C2%A0%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20lab%20members%20are%20seen%20surrounding%20the%20developed%20carbon-sequestered%20building%20materials%2C%20which%20were%20manufactured%20using%20additive%20manufacturing.%C2%A0%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Feh0cdld8_the-material-group_625x300_02_April_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lab%20members%20are%20seen%20surrounding%20the%20developed%20carbon-sequestered%20building%20materials%2C%20which%20were%20manufactured%20using%20additive%20manufacturing.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20The%20MatERIAL%20group%2C%20CST%2C%20IISc%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCO2%20utilisation%20and%20sequestration%20can%20be%20a%20scalable%20and%20feasible%20technology%20for%20manufacturing%20low-carbon%20prefabricated%20building%20products%20while%20being%20aligned%20with%20the%20nation's%20decarbonisation%20targets%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiisc.ac.in%2Fevents%2Fpaving-new-paths-for-sustainable-construction%2F%5C%22%3Eexplains%20Dr%20Souradeep%20Gupta%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whose%20lab%20is%20carrying%20out%20these%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20innovative%20process%20boasts%20a%2020-22%25%20increase%20in%20the%20material's%20compressive%20strength.%20Additionally%2C%20injecting%20CO2%20into%20clay%20soil%2C%20commonly%20found%20at%20construction%20sites%2C%20improves%20its%20interaction%20with%20cement%20and%20lime.%20This%20not%20only%20stabilises%20the%20clay%20but%20also%20enhances%20its%20overall%20engineering%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Gupta's%20team's%20research%20extends%20further.%20They've%20explored%20incorporating%20captured%20CO2%20into%20excavated%20soil%20to%20create%20cement-lime-soil%20composites%2C%20potentially%20replacing%20up%20to%20half%20of%20the%20fine%20aggregates%20typically%20used%20in%20mortar.%20This%20technique%20promotes%20the%20formation%20of%20calcium%20carbonate%20crystals%2C%20leading%20to%20improved%20strength%20and%20reduced%20pore%20space.%20Exposing%20these%20materials%20to%20CO2%20further%20accelerates%20curing%20and%20increases%20early-age%20strength%20by%2030%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20have%20also%20developed%203D-printable%20materials%20using%20stabilised%20excavated%20soil%20combined%20with%20binders%20like%20cement%2C%20slag%2C%20and%20fly%20ash.%20These%20materials%20offer%20superior%20printability%2C%20potentially%20reducing%20the%20need%20for%20cement%20and%20sand%20by%20up%20to%2050%25%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFuture%20research%20will%20focus%20on%20the%20impact%20of%20industrial%20flue%20gas%20on%20these%20materials'%20properties%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20industrial%20applications%20and%20potentially%20revising%20standards%20for%20cement-based%20construction%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712047740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fd1mrj8h8_sand_625x300_02_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsand-substitute-developed-by-indian-scientists-for-eco-friendly-construction-5358009%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20team%20has%20also%20developed%203D-printable%20materials%20made%20of%20excavated%20soil%20stabilised%20with%20a%20combination%20of%20binders%20like%20Portland%20cement%2C%20blast%20furnace%20