B%20and%20demanded%20immediate%20action%20against%20%26quot%3Bfalse%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmisleading%26quot%3B%20advertisements.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20very%20unfortunate...%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20had%20said%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20also%20urged%20the%20centre%20to%20find%20a%20remedy%20to%20the%20issue%20of%20misleading%20medical%20ads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20today%20also%20ripped%20into%20Ramdev%20and%20Balakrishna%20for%20the%20causal%20manner%20in%20which%20an%20affidavit%20-%20offering%20an%20unconditional%20apology%20for%20the%20ads%20-%20was%20filed%20last%20month.%20A%20furious%20court%20called%20the%20affidavit%20%26quot%3Bindefensible%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bhumbug%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20even%20suggested%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20could%20be%20guilt%20of%20perjury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpatanjali-acharya-balkrishna-supreme-court-intention-only-to-patanjalis-apology-to-supreme-court-in-ads-case-5280295%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPatanjali's%20Apology%20Day%20After%20Court%20Summons%20Ramdev%20In%20Ads%20Case%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20should%20have%20made%20sure%20the%20solemn%20undertaking%20should%20have%20been%20in%20letter%20and%20spirit.%20We%20can%20also%20say%20we%20are%20'sorry'...%20for%20not%20accepting%20it%20(the%20apology)...%20it%20is%20more%20of%20a%20lip%20service%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20angered%20that%20Patanjali%20had%2C%20prima%20facie%2C%20continued%20to%20run%20ads%20ruled%20as%20misleading%20last%20year.%20The%20claim%20that%20the%20company's%20media%20unit%20was%20unaware%20of%20the%20court%20order%20was%20dismissed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2