0Costs%20Rs%202000%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBengaluru%20is%20infamous%20for%20its%20traffic%20and%20hours-long%20traffic%20jams.%20People%20keep%20sharing%20about%20the%20traffic%20nightmare%20and%20less%20availability%20of%20public%20transport.%20Due%20to%20this%2C%20many%20people%20take%20private%20cabs%20and%20are%20dependent%20on%20cab%20aggregators%20like%20Ola%20and%20Uber.%20A%20woman%20recently%20took%20to%20social%20media%20to%20share%20her%20experience%20of%20booking%20a%20cab%20from%20Bengaluru%20airport%20to%20the%20city.%20The%20user%2C%20Manasvi%20Sharma%2C%20shared%20that%20she%20took%20a%20flight%20from%20Pune%20to%20Bengaluru%20for%20just%20Rs%203%2C500.%20However%2C%20travelling%20from%20Bengaluru%20Airport%20to%20the%20city%20cost%20her%20around%20Rs%202%2C000.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shared%20a%20screenshot%20of%20Uber%20charging%20nearly%20Rs%202%2C000%20to%20%C2%A0Rs%202%2C700%20for%20different%20types%20of%20cabs%20for%20a%20trip%20from%20Kempegowda%20International%20Airport%20to%20the%20city.%20%26quot%3BI%20booked%20flight%20for%203.5k%20from%20Pune%20to%20Bangalore.%20And%20then%2C%20a%20cab%20for%202k%20from%20Bangalore%20airport%20to%20my%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sharma%20wrote%20in%20the%20caption%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20booked%20flight%20for%203.5k%20from%20Pune%20to%20Bangalore.%3Cbr%3E%5CnAnd%20then%2C%20a%20cab%20for%202k%20from%20Bangalore%20airport%20to%20my%20home%F0%9F%92%80%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUber_India%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Uber_India%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FwZyzOpOvHF%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FwZyzOpOvHF%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Manasvi%20Sharma%20(%40manasvisharmaaa)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmanasvisharmaaa%2Fstatus%2F1774682133627576486%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3