%20sent%20back%20to%20his%20cell%20at%2012%20noon%20and%20he%20will%20have%20to%20stay%20there%20till%203%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20doctors%20and%20medical%20staff%20available%2024%2F7%20in%20case%20of%20an%20emergency.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20is%20a%20diabetic%2C%20will%20have%20regular%20check-ups%20during%20his%20imprisonment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20has%20also%20been%20allowed%20to%20carry%20some%20toffees%20in%20case%20of%20a%20dip%20in%20his%20sugar%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArvind%20Kejriwal%20slept%20on%20his%20own%20bed%2C%20which%20was%20different%20from%20the%20regular%20one%20provided%20by%20the%20jail%20authorities.%20He%20used%20his%20own%20bed%20linen%20given%20his%20weakened%20immune%20system%20that%20puts%20him%20at%20risk%20of%20potentially%20severe%20allergic%20reactions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20sources%20in%20the%20Tihar%20jail%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20has%20been%20provided%20with%20copies%20of%20the%20Ramayan%2C%20Shrimad%20Bhagvad%20Gita%2C%20and%20How%20Prime%20Ministers%20Decide%20-%20a%20book%20by%20journalist%20Neerja%20Chowdhury%20as%20per%20the%20court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20been%20allowed%20to%20keep%20a%20chair%20and%20a%20table%20in%20the%20cell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20chief%20was%20arrested%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20on%20March%2021.%20AAP%20has%20maintained%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20change%20in%20the%20leadership%2C%20even%20if%20that%20means%20Mr%20Kerjriwal%20functions%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20from%20the%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712042820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fb7o16o6_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_27_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-arrest-arvind-kejriwal-arrested-delhi-liquor-policy-case-arvind-kejriwal-sent-to-tihar-jail-but-this-isnt-his-1st-ti