%2Farticleshow%2F108966144.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108966144.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EVijay%20Deverakonda%20and%20Mrunal%20Thakur's%20%26quot%3BFamily%20Star%26quot%3B%20has%20struggled%20to%20make%20an%20impact%20at%20the%20box%20office%2C%20both%20in%20India%20and%20the%20USA.%20Despite%20excitement%20from%20the%20actors%2C%20advance%20booking%20in%20the%20USA%20has%20been%20below%20expectations%2C%20with%20just%203200%20tickets%20sold%20out%20of%20400%20shows%2C%20leading%20to%20concerns%20over%20its%20performance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fvijay-deverakonda-and-mrunal-thakurs-family-star-takes-a-below-par-start-in-usa%2Farticleshow%2F108966144.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Atishi%20Claims%20BJP%20Switch%20Offer%2C%20Says%20These%20AAP%20Leaders%20To%20Be%20Arrested%20Soon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFour%20more%20senior%20leaders%20of%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20are%20set%20to%20be%20arrested%20over%20the%20next%20two%20months%2C%20Delhi%20minister%20Atishi%20alleged%20today%2C%20accusing%20the%20BJP%20of%20using%20central%20agencies%20in%20its%20attempt%20to%20crush%20AAP.%C2%A0The%20ruling%20party%2C%20she%20alleged%2C%20plans%20to%20arrest%20her%2C%20Delhi%20minister%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%2C%20AAP%20MP%20Raghav%20Chadha%20and%20party%20MLA%20Durgesh%20Pathak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20has%20approached%20me%20through%20someone%20very%20close.%20They%20have%20asked%20me%20to%20join%20the%20BJP%20and%20said%20this%20will%20save%20my%20political%20career.%20They%20have%20threatened%20that%20if%20I%20don't%20switch%20over%2C%20ED%20(Enforcement%20Directorate)%20will%20arrest%20me%20within%20a%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20person%20who%20approached%20her%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20BJP%20had%20said%20that%20the%20ruling%20party%20had%20%26quot%3Bmade%20up%20its%20mind%20on%20crushing%20everyone%20in%20AAP%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%2C%20they%20put%20everyone%20in%20AAP's%20leadership%20in%20jail.%20Satyendra%20Jain%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20Sanjay%20Singh%20and%20now%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20have%20been%20arrested.%20The%20BJP's%20plan%20is%20to%20arrest%20four%20more%20AAP%20leaders%20in%20the%20next%20two%20months.%20They%20will%20arrest%20me%2C%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%2C%20Durgesh%20Pathak%20and%20Raghav%20Chadha%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20Ms%20Atishi%20said%2C%20had%20thought%20that%20the%20party%20would%20splinter%20after%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20arrest.%20%26quot%3BBut%20after%20the%20rally%20in%20Ramlila%20Maidan%20Sunday%2C%20the%20BJP%20thinks%20the%20arrest%20of%20four%20leaders%20was%20not%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20minister%20claimed%20that%20she%20had%20received%20information%20that%20ED%20may%20raid%20her%20and%20her%20relatives'%20homes%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20soldiers%2C%20we%20won't%20be%20cowed%20down%20by%20BJP's%20threats.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Atishi%20referred%20to%20the%20ED's%20submission%20in%20court%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20had%20said%20AAP's%20former%20communication%20boss%20Vijay%20Nair%20reported%20to%20her%20and%20Mr%20Bharadwaj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20information%20is%20already%20in%20ED's%20and%20CBI's%20chargesheets.%20It%20is%20possible%20that%20ED%20took%20our%20names%20so%20that%20they%20proceed%20on%20arresting%20the%20second%20line%20of%20AAP%20leadership%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20described%20the%20AAP%20leader's%20allegations%20as%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%26quot%3B.%20Party%20leader%20RP%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20too%20can%20say%20that%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20called%20me%20up%20and%20requested%20me%20to%20protect%20them%20from%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20who%20wants%20to%20put%20them%20behind%20bars%20and%20make%20Sunita%20Kejriwal%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20This%20is%20their%20internal%20tussle%2C%20which%20is%20coming%20out%20again%20and%20again%20in%20different%20forms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20truth%20is%20that%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20all%20whose%20names%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20matter.%20It%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20fight%20for%20the%20CM%20post%20has%20begun%20in%20AAP.%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20and%20Atishi%20are%20on%20one%20side%20and%20Sunita%20Kejriwal%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20are%20on%20the%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Atishi's%20allegations%20and%20the%20BJP's%20counter%20are%20the%20latest%20in%20the%20heated%20exchanges%20between%20AAP%20and%20BJP%20leaders%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20related%20to%20Delhi's%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20been%20remanded%20in%20judicial%20custody%20till%20April%2015%20and%20moved%20to%20Delhi's%20Tihar%20jail.%20The%20ED%20has%20said%20he%20is%20not%20cooperating%20in%20the%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712041320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fjure4tp8_aap-leaders-split_625x300_02_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fatishi-saurabh-bharadwaj-arvind-kejriwal-atishi-claims-offer-to-join-bjp-says-4-more-aap-leaders-to-be-arrested-5356952%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20more%20senior%20leaders%20of%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20are%20set%20to%20be%20arrested%20over%20the%20next%20two%20months%2C%20Delhi%20minister%20Atishi%20alleged%20today%2C%20ac