n%20officer%2C%20Tan%20said%20he%20was%20tasked%20with%20training%20the%20new%20recruits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20found%20purpose%20in%20what%20I%20was%20doing%20then.%20I%20got%20to%20interact%20with%20new%20soldiers%20and%20helped%20to%20make%20their%20training%20more%20interesting%2C%26quot%3B%20Tan%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThat%20was%20when%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20career.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20also%20the%20case%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-army-for-private-sector-have-no-regrets-serving-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJiahui%20Ong%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2026%2C%20when%20she%20decided%20to%20call%20it%20quits%20with%20the%20army.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOng%20told%20BI%20that%20she%20had%20mixed%20feelings%20when%20she%20decided%20to%20leave%20the%20military%20after%20serving%20for%20five%20years.%20She%20said%20it%20took%20her%20nearly%20three%20months%20to%20decide%20if%20she%20wanted%20to%20leave%20her%20comfort%20zone%20in%20the%20army.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20in%20the%20army%20and%20having%20to%20leave%20was%20very%20difficult.%20A%20lot%20of%20my%20identity%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20self-worth%2C%20was%20actually%20built%20when%20I%20was%20in%20the%20force%2C%26quot%3B%20Ong%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20things%20were%20a%20lot%20different%20after%20they%20made%20the%20leap%20into%20the%20private%20sector.%20Ong%2C%20who%20took%20up%20a%20new%20career%20in%20banking%2C%20said%20working%20at%20DBS%20Bank%20was%20a%20full%20180-degree%20change%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20main%20difference%20I%20observed%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%20versus%20the%20army%20was%20that%20everyone%20in%20the%20military%20appears%20to%20be%20working%20toward%20the%20same%20agenda%20and%20objectives%2C%26quot%3B%20Ong%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20everyone%20has%20their%20own%20agendas%20and%20personal%20goals%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20contin