0grandfather%20used%20to%20serve%20him.%20I%20have%20seen%20and%20heard%20stories%20of%20how%20my%20grandfather%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20Independence%20fight.%20Many%20times%2C%20the%20freedom%20fighters%20would%20stop%20by%2C%20and%20he%20would%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F284636%2Findia-food-maps-mithai-spices-chai-cuisine-mangoes-pics%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecook%20a%20meal%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20article%20in%20the%20digital%20repository%20also%20highlighted%20an%20incident%20in%201930%20when%20Subhas%20Chandra%20Bose%20and%20fellow%20freedom%20fighters%20visited%20the%20hotel%20and%20raised%20spirited%20slogans%20like%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EJai%20Hind%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EVande%20Mataram%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20Panda%20enthusiastically%20joined%20in.%20It%20sheds%20light%20on%20Mangobindo%E2%80%99s%20generosity%20as%20he%20provided%20food%20to%20hundreds%20of%20those%20who%20were%20starving%20during%20the%20Bengal%20famine%20of%201943.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20these%2C%20Arunangshu%20has%20heard%20many%20stories%20of%20how%20Bose%20loved%20the%20%3Cem%3Epuishaak-er%20chochchori%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Emurighanta%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20Bengali%20fish%20delicacy).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20day%20begins%20in%20the%20City%20of%20Joy%2C%20the%20first%20trickle%20of%20guests%20begins%20to%20enter%20the%20Swadhin%20Bharat%20Hindu%20Hotel%2C%20which%20is%20carrying%20the%20baton%20of%20its%20legacy%20forward%2C%20not%20just%20in%20its%20food%20but%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F294513%2Frare-pictures-of-india-history-freedom-struggle-independence-day%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20tales%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20every%20guest%20is%20treated%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3