-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20is%20there%20a%20cap%20on%20abortion%20limits%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201996%2C%20after%20completing%20his%20MD%20in%20gynaecology%2C%20Dr%20Nikhil%20started%20practising%20as%20an%20obstetrician-gynaecologist%20in%20Mumbai-based%20hospitals.%20During%20the%20course%2C%20he%20would%20meet%20a%20large%20number%20of%20patients%20with%20pregnancies%20beyond%2020%20weeks%20who%20desired%20to%20get%20it%20terminated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20neurological%20and%20cardiac%20abnormalities%20are%20detected%20a%20little%20after%2020%20weeks%20of%20the%20foetus%20developing%2C%20most%20other%20abnormalities%20can%20be%20detected%20before%20this%20time%20frame%20if%20there%20is%20access%20to%20healthcare%20at%20the%20right%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdr-nikhil-1711970967.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Nikhil%20points%20out%20that%20owing%20to%20poor%20health%20services%2C%20diagnosis%20of%20abnormalities%20in%20foetus%20of%20rural%20women%20is%20delayed.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdr-nikhil-1711970967.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdr-nikhil-1711970967-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdr-nikhil-1711970967-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdr-nikhil-1711970967-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdr-nikhil-1711970967-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346150%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Nikhil%20points%20out%20that%20owing%20to%20poor%20health%20services%2C%20diagnosis%20of%20abnormalities%20in%20the%20foetus%20of%20rural%20women%20is%20delayed.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20rural%20areas%2C%20women%20have%20to%20take%20a%20bus%20to%20reach%20the%20nearest%20taluk-level%20government%20hospitals%20for%20check%20ups.%20Owing%20to%20poor%20services%2C%20it%20remains%20uncertain%20whether%20the%20sonography%20will%20be%20performed%20on%20these%20patients%20on%20that%20given%20day.%20By%20the%20time%20it%E2%80%99s%20done%20for%20any%20abnormalities%20to%20be%20detected%2C%20it%20is%20too%20late%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Nikhil%20points%20out%20that%20in%20such%20cases%2C%20if%20the%20woman%20is%20forced%20to%20give%20birth%2C%20she%20is%20made%20to%20take%20the%20penalty%20for%20those%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBesides%2C%20there%20are%20cases%20where%20women%20in%20their%20late%2040s%20miss%20out%20on%20menstruation%2C%20and%20they%20are%20advised%20to%20not%20worry%20as%20they%20are%20getting%20closer%20to%20menopause.%20One%20fine%20day%2C%20they%20find%20out%20that%20they%20are%20already%2022%20weeks%20pregnant%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F62683%2Fabortion-laws-india-supreme-court-rape-survivor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eterminating%20pregnancies%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebeyond%2020%20weeks%20a%20criminal%20offence%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20gone%20through%20the%20MTP%20Act%20multiple%20times%20and%20thoroughly%20researched%20the%20topic%20only%20to%20find%20out%20that%20the%20set%20limit%20was%20arbitrary.%20There%20was%20no%20reason%20to%20support%20why%20it%20was%20set%20to%2020%20weeks%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Nikhil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20if%20a%20woman%20is%2019%20weeks%20pregnant%2C%20then%20doctors%20will%20not%20even%20blink%20before%20terminating%20the%20pregnancy%20but%20when%20she%20is%20at%2021%20weeks%2C%20that%20becomes%20a%20problem.%20The%20termination%20of%20pregnancy%20is%20primarily%20meant%20for%20major%20and%20substantial%20abnormalities.%20You%20are%20refusing%20it%20because%20she%20has%20crossed%20over%20some%20arbitrary%20limit.%20As%20a%20specialist%2C%20I%20know%20that%20it%20is%20safe%20to%20terminate%20the%20pregnancy%20beyond%2020%20weeks.%20We%20are%20not%20in%201971%20anymore!%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-1-1711970332.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Nikhil%20opined%20it%20was%20unfair%20to%20punish%20women%20by%20forcing%20them%20to%20give%20birth%20to%20intellectually%20or%20physically%20disabled%20infants.%C2%A0%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-1-1711970332.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-1-1711970332-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-1-1711970332-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-1-1711970332-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-1-1711970332-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346147%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Nikhil%20opined%20it%20was%20unfair%20to%20punish%20women%20by%20forcing%20them%20to%20give%20birth%20to%20intellectually%20or%20physically%20disabled%20infants.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Nikhil%20reached%20out%20to%20national-level%20medical%20bodies%20to%20draw%20their%20attention%20to%20the%20need%20to%20amend%20the%20MTP%20Act%20and%20extend%20the%20permissible%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F286289%2Fsister-duo-activists-fight-female-foeticide-women-education-health-empowerment%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabortion%20term%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20that%20discussion%20became%20limited%20to%20medical%20conferences%20only.%20It%20was%20high%20time%20that%20we%20convinced%20lawmakers%2C%20judges%2C%20and%20policymakers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20in%202008%2C%20Dr%20Nikhil%20met%20Niketa%20Mehta%2C%20who%20was%2024%20weeks%20pregnant%20with%20a%20baby%20with%20multiple%20congenital%20heart%20abnormalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisheartened%20by%20another%20such%20case%2C%20Dr%20Nikhil%20and%20the%20patient%20went%20on%20to%20challenge%20the%20law.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20judiciary%20when%20a%20doctor%20and%20a%20patient%20got%20together%20to%20challenge%20a%20law.%20Usually%2C%20both%20fight%20against%20each%20other%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20their%20plea%20was%20rejected.%20But%20this%20did%20not%20deter%20his%20resolve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%2014-year-long%20fight%20for%20abortion%20rights%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgain%20in%202016%2C%20Dr%20Nikhil%20was%20put%20in%20a%20similar%20situation.%20%E2%80%9CA%20minor%20rape%20survivor%20was%20brought%20to%20me%20by%20a%20non-profit%20organisation.%20She%20was%2024%20weeks%20pregnant%20and%20the%20foetus%E2%80%99%20brain%20was%20not%20developed.%20In%20such%20cases%2C%20the%20foetus%20stays%20alive%20till%20the%20umbilical%20cord%20is%20intact.%20As%20soon%20as%20the%20cord%20is%20clamped%20and%20cut%2C%20it%20dies.%20Given%20the%20sensitivity%2C%20nobody%20wanted%20to%20touch%20this%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20a%20sigh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20justice%20for%20these%20women.%20He%20got%20his%20first%20breakthrough%20in%20the%20apex%20court%20when%20he%20garnered%20the%20support%20of%20320%20women%20who%20had%20abnormal%20foetuses%2C%20were%20minor%20rape%20survivors%20and%20from%20low%20socio-economic%20backgrounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-3-1711970661.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202019%2C%20Dr%20Nikhil%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20justice%20for%20women.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-3-1711970661.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-3-1711970661-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-3-1711970661-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-3-1711970661-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-3-1711970661-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346149%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202019%2C%20Dr%20Nikhil%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20justice%20for%20women.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Nikhil%2C%20who%20also%20holds%20a%20law%20degree%2C%20burnt%20the%20midnight%20oil%20in%20the%20preparation%20of%20this%20case.%20From%20drafting%2C%20coordinating%20with%20the%20right%20contacts%2C%20creating%20adequate%20evidence%2C%20and%20responding%20to%20medical%20as%20well%20as%20legal%20questions%2C%20he%20meticulously%20planned%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20passed%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1705381%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Rajya%2520Sabha%2520has%2520approved%2Con%252017th%2520March%25202020.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMedical%20Termination%20of%20Pregnancy%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202021%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20amend%20the%20MTP%20Act%201971.%20The%20Bill%20was%20approved%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20enhanced%20the%20upper%20gestation%20limit%20from%2020%20to%2024%20weeks%20for%20special%20categories%20of%20women%20which%20will%20be%20defined%20in%20the%20amendments%20of%20the%20Act.%20It%20would%20include%20survivors%20of%20rape%2C%20victims%20of%20incest%2C%20and%20other%20vulnerable%20women%20such%20as%20disabled%20women%20and%20minors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20again%20an%20arbitrary%20limit%2C%2024%20weeks%20is%20still%20a%20pretty%20decent%20time%20frame%20to%20detect%20abnormalities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20mentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20his%20patients%2C%20this%20judgement%20has%20been%20extremely%20satisfying%20for%20Dr%20Nikhil%20personally%2C%20who%20has%20fought%20multiple%20challenges%20and%20threats%20in%20various%20forms%20in%20his%2014-year%20crusade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20doctor%2C%20we%20see%20families%20starting%20with%20the%20birth%20of%20their%20children.%20We%20become%20a%20part%20of%20these%20units%20as%20they%20remember%20us%20all%20the%20time.%20I%20get%2030%20such%20cases%20every%20month.%20But%20when%20you%20are%20able%20to%20contribute%20towards%20a%20larger%20policy%20change%2C%20you%20are%20able%20to%20impact%20lakhs%20and%20crores%20of%20lives%20known%20and%20unknown%20to%20you.%20That%E2%80%99s%20a%20whole%20new%20level%20of%20satisfaction%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edite