ow%20to%20different%20cultures.%20Given%20this%20background%2C%20our%20core%20will%20always%20remain%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20joining%20Adukale%20in%202017%2C%20Bharat%20became%20director%20in%202019%2C%20and%20subsequently%20the%20CEO%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Adukale%20enjoys%20an%20extensive%20selection%20of%2056%20products%2C%20available%20across%2020%20stores%20throughout%20Bengaluru%20and%20Mysuru.%20%E2%80%9CAdditionally%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20established%20a%20strong%20online%20presence%2C%20ensuring%20our%20offerings%20are%20accessible%20to%20customers%20far%20and%20wide.%20As%20Adukale%20continues%20to%20grow%20and%20expand%20its%20reach%2C%20it%20remains%20rooted%20in%20its%20core%20mission%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322885%2Fkarnataka-shivaranjini-started-suggi-oota-south-indian-restaurant-in-california%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshowcasing%20the%20rich%20heritage%20of%20Karnataka%20cuisine%20to%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20delicious%20product%20at%20a%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20range%20of%20products%20currently%20comprises%20RTE%20foods%20like%20%3Cem%3Epoha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Eupma%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Egojjavalakki%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Ebisi%20bele%20bath%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20spicy%2C%20rice-based%20dish)%2C%20blended%20spices%20like%3Cem%3E%20chutney%3C%2Fem%3E%20powders%2C%20%3Cem%3Esambar%20%3C%2Fem%3Epowder%2C%20%3Cem%3Etarkaari%20gojjina%3C%2Fem%3E%20powder%20(spice%20mix%20to%20prepare%20%3Cem%3Egojju%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Enamkeens%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20savouries%20like%20%3Cem%3Enippattu%3C%2Fem%3E%20(crispy%20deep%20fried%20rice%20crackers)%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekayi%20kodubale%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20popular%20deep-fried%20snack%20from%20Karnataka%20made%20using%20rice%20flour%2C%20coconut%2C%20ground%20roasted%20gram%20powder).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20t