%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20visit%20the%20homestay%2C%20you%20can%20expect%20serenity%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20heritage.%20The%20nature%20surrounding%20us%20will%20fill%20you%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20peace%2C%20and%20our%20authentic%20meals%20will%20nourish%20your%20soul%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rajchandar%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20homestay%20is%20not%20just%20a%20marvel%20of%20culture%20but%20also%20a%20great%20example%20of%20sustainability.%20From%20composting%20their%20waste%20to%20implementing%20measures%20to%20recharge%20groundwater%2C%20the%20mud%20homestay%20is%20raising%20the%20bar%20for%20nature-friendly%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInspiration%20from%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20home%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Kanyakumari%2C%20Rajchandar%20is%20a%20geo-data%20scientist%20who%20has%20spent%20the%20majority%20of%20his%20life%20around%20environmentalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSpending%20so%20much%20time%20around%20them%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20my%20home%20as%20aligned%20with%20nature%20as%20possible.%20I%20had%20always%20been%20concerned%20about%20the%20degradation%20of%20our%20environment%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20contribute%20to%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajchandar%20fondly%20recalls%20his%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20home%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F273684%2Fbest-ecofriendly-homestay-munnar-book-treehouse%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurrounded%20by%20greenery.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-12-1711118400.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20homestay%20has%20artefacts%2