ay%20they%20treated%20us.%20The%20food%2C%20their%20accommodating%20behaviour%20made%20our%20stay%20very%20enjoyable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscussing%20future%20plans%2C%20Rajchandar%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20really%20want%20to%20expand%20the%20property%20as%20many%20people%20want%20to%20stay%2C%20but%20we%20are%20often%20fully%20booked.%20We%20also%20aim%20to%20incorporate%20more%20sustainable%20measures%20like%20solar%20energy%20into%20the%20current%20homestay.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20book%20your%20stay%20at%20this%20Rajchandar%E2%80%99s%20homestay%20by%20reaching%20them%20at%209360946642%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20Pictures%20Credit%3A%20Rajchandar)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711524048000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-12-1711118400.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D345629%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Looking%20for%20the%20best%20homestays%20in%20Kanyakumari%3F%20Rajchandar%20Padmanaban%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Naga%20Jeyalakshmi%2C%20built%20Muthunandhini%20Palace%20as%20a%20heritage%20home%20where%20sustainability%20meets%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20traditional%20architecture.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345629%2Fmuthunandhini-palace-kanyakumari-ecofriendly-homestay-chettinad-architecture-tamil-nadu-travel-destination%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98We%20Should%20Experiment%E2%80%99%3A%20Farmer%E2%80%99s%20Switch%20From%20Wheat%20to%20Turmeric%20Doubled%20Her%20Income%20to%20Rs%2012%20Lakh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELocated%20on%20the%20bank%20of%20the%20Narmada%20river%2C%20Narmadapuram%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20is%20famous%20for%20its%20fertile%20black%20soil%20that%20yields%20high-quality%20wheat