0of%20India%20are%20empty.%20People%20are%20moving%20away.%20Village%20tourism%20will%20not%20only%20help%20generate%20employment%20for%20the%20locals%20but%20give%20them%20a%20reason%20to%20stay%20back%20in%20the%20villages.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESawant%20also%20started%20a%20textile%20upscaling%20project%20in%20the%20state%20wherein%20she%20encouraged%2060%20women%20to%20earn%20through%20patchwork%20items%20such%20as%20quilts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20fascinating%20is%20that%20Sawant%E2%80%99s%20slew%20of%20projects%20are%20not%20only%20focused%20on%20empowering%20women%20but%20doing%20this%20while%20helping%20city%20folk%20have%20an%20unparalleled%20holiday%20experience.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20rural%20tourism%20project%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20She%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20village%20called%20%E2%80%98Veerapuram%E2%80%99%20was%20given%20to%20us%20to%20develop.%20The%20village%20is%20a%20hotspot%20for%20the%20migratory%20birds%20that%20come%20to%20nest%20here%20from%20August%20to%20January%20every%20year.%20Over%20thousands%20of%20these%20birds%20flock%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESawant%20organised%2020%20women%20into%20self-help%20groups%20that%20would%20conduct%20and%20benefit%20from%20bird%20tourism.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20women%20were%20trained%20to%20take%20the%20tourists%20around%20the%20village%2C%20explain%20to%20them%20about%20these%20birds%20and%20their%20migration%20patterns%20and%20show%20them%20their%20nests.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Sawant%20looks%20back%20on%20how%20she%20has%20succeeded%20in%20bridging%20the%20gap%20between%20tourists%20looking%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F308710%2Ftentgram-provides-experiential-travel-across-india-wayanad-kashmir-meghalaya-himachal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperiential%20travel%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20one%20side%20and%20villagers%20looking%20to%20earn%20on%20the%20other%2C%20s