A0%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Issac%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20began%20with%20involuntary%20shaking%20of%20his%20hands%20without%20anyone%20taking%20note%20of%20it.%20We%20waited%20for%20months%20before%20seeking%20medical%20input.%20He%20was%20put%20on%20a%20medicine%20called%20Syndopa%20that%20continued%20throughout%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20life%20along%20with%20certain%20vitamin%20supplements.%20While%20he%20worked%20for%20another%20year%20after%20his%20first%20diagnosis%2C%20driving%20a%20car%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20things%20he%20had%20to%20give%20up%2C%20and%20subsequently%2C%20his%20job%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20some%20time%2C%20Issac%E2%80%99s%20father%20was%20compelled%20to%20move%20to%20a%20small%20town%20in%20Kerala%20and%20live%20with%20their%20joint%20family.%20Since%20then%2C%20they%20had%20to%20engage%20in%20%E2%80%98steady%20management%E2%80%99%20of%20his%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20received%20little%20guidance%20on%20what%20diet%20or%20lifestyle%20would%20help%20him%20cope%20better.%20Living%20in%20a%20small%20town%20in%20Kerala%2C%20access%20to%20high-quality%20neurological%20experts%20was%20also%20limited.%20Our%20family%20and%20I%20accepted%20the%20status%20quo%20and%20slowly%20he%20withdrew%20from%20other%20social%20activities.%20He%20wanted%20to%20resume%20work%20in%20some%20way%2C%20but%20the%20shaking%20of%20the%20hands%20transferred%20to%20the%20legs%20as%20well%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20and%20he%20had%20to%20have%20someone%20around%20for%20mobility%20around%20the%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20a%20point%2C%20the%20medication%20did%20little%20to%20improve%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20quality%20of%20life%3B%20seeing%20it%20deteriorate%20like%20that%20despite%20the%20medication%20had%20a%20profound%20impact%20on%20Isaac.%20Tragically%2C%20he%20passed%20away%20in%202020%20amid%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Rahul%20Krishnan%2C%20who%20comes%20from%20a%20large%20joint%20family%20in%20Ernakulam%2C%20Kerala%2C%20also%20witnessed%20firsthand%20the%20struggles%20of%20loneliness%20and%20isolation%20among%20his%20older%20relatives%2C%20particularly%20those%20dealing%20with%20neurodegenerative%20conditions.%20With%20the%20added%20strain%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20there%20was%20news%20every%20day%20of%20someone%E2%80%99s%20cognitive%20health%20in%20the%20family%20deteriorating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Rahul%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20come%20from%20a%20large%20joint%20family%20in%20Kerala.%20Like%20me%2C%20many%20of%20my%20cousins%20and%20friends%20ventured%20away%20from%20home%20in%20pursuit%20of%20better%20educational%20and%20career%20prospects.%20With%20the%20rise%20of%20nuclear%20families%2C%20meeting%20elders%20became%20a%20yearly%20affair%20at%20best.%20But%20witnessing%20the%20rapid%20ageing%20and%20forgetfulness%20of%20our%20loved%20ones%20has%20always%20made%20me%20wonder%20why%20there%20are%20no%20tools%20for%20early%20detection%20of%20memory%20decline.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20encouraged%20my%20father%20to%20play%20sudoku%20and%20solve%20puzzle%20books%20to%20keep%20his%20mind%20sharp%20and%20active%2C%20I%20recognised%20a%20latent%20concern%20in%20almost%20every%20family%20like%20mine.%20The%20realisation%20that%20there%20is%20a%20significant%20gap%20in%20awareness%20and%20access%20to%20resources%20aimed%20at%20understanding%20and%20arresting%20cognitive%20decline%20served%20as%20a%20key%20driving%20force%20behind%20the%20inception%20of%20%E2%80%98Ivory%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20meeting%20each%20other%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20July%202022%20during%20a%20residency%20programme%20for%20aspiring%20entrepreneurs%20run%20by%20Antler%2C%20an%20early-stage%20venture%20capitalist%20(VC)%20firm%2C%20Issac%20and%20Rahul%20would%2