g%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIvory-Representational-1711111266.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taking%20care%20of%20your%20parents'%20brain%20health%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIvory-Representational-1711111266.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIvory-Representational-1711111266-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIvory-Representational-1711111266-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIvory-Representational-1711111266-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIvory-Representational-1711111266-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345586%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9COur%20starting%20point%20was%20to%20build%20something%20that%20would%20help%20parents%20feel%20less%20isolated%20and%20lonely%20as%20they%20stayed%20away%20from%20their%20children.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20scale%20of%20the%20problem%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20September%202023%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CEstimates%20based%20on%20a%20recent%20multi-centric%20study%20reveal%20a%20dementia%20prevalence%20rate%20of%207.4%25%20among%20those%20aged%2060%20years%20and%20above%2C%20translating%20to%20nearly%209%20lakh%20Indians%20currently%20living%20with%20dementia.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20goes%20on%20to%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20an%20estimated%2088%20lakh%20in%202016%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337126%2Fmonitors-for-elderly-hemesh-chadalavada-invents-device-for-dementia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevalence%20of%20dementia%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20projected%20to%20increase%20to%201.7%20crore%20by%202036.%20The%20study%20titled%20%E2%80%98Prevalence%20of%20dementia%20in%20India%3A%20National%20and%20State%20estimates%20from%20a%20nationwide%20study%E2%80%99%20was%20published%20in%20July%20this%20year%20%5B2023%5D%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAlzheimer%E2%80%99s%20and%20Dementia%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20journal%20of%20the%20Alzheimer%E2%80%99s%20Association.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20experts%20at%20Ivory%2C%20%E2%80%9CLatest%20research%20estimates%20show%20that%20one%20person%20in%20India%20faces%20the%20risk%20of%20dementia%20every%2020%20seconds.%20Contributing%20factors%20such%20as%20loneliness%2C%20increased%20nuclear%20families%20and%20sedentary%20lifestyles%20have%20added%20to%20the%20problem.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20their%20research%2C%20%E2%80%9CLatest%20reports%20show%20that%20cases%20have%20increased%20from%20an%20estimated%205.3%20million%20in%202020%20to%208.8%20million%20in%202023.%20Furthermore%2C%20adults%20aged%2050%20to%2070%2C%20even%20with%20mild%20cognitive%20impairment%2C%20face%20a%201%20in%203%20chance%20of%20progressing%20to%20dementia%20within%20five%20years%2C%20underscoring%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20heightened%20dialogue%20and%20action%20in%20neuro%20health.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20subject%2C%20Issac%2C%20co-founder%20and%20CEO%20at%20Ivory%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHistorically%2C%20there%20has%20been%20insufficient%20attention%20and%20understanding%20of%20dementia%2C%20especially%20in%20India.%20The%20lack%20of%20symptom%20identification%20tools%20combined%20with%20scant%20access%20to%20high-quality%20neurological%20advice%20at%20the%20right%20time%20makes%20this%20a%20pressing%20problem%20for%20every%20Indian%20household%20with%20an%20ageing%20parent.%20Urban%20seniors%2C%20partic